nodes.text: Sai'torr Kal Fas was a Saurin female from the planet Durkteel. She was the bodyguard of her cousin Hrchek Kal Fas, a Saurin droid trader.
Sai'torr also taught battle skills to those who proved themselves worthy. She worked for the Rebellion as a scout and trainer. Sai'torr Kal Fas was near Nabrun Leids, Yerka Mig and Takeel.
Although uncredited, Sai'torr Kal Fas was played by Barbara Frankland.
